task.summary: Fixed /stats not working for offline players.
Made list that contains all kits public for api.
Fix percentage format when sending a message.
Setting precision for double on print format.
Having KD format to 2 decimal places.
Added another method to get PSO from String and not Player object.
Fixed null pointer exception from toUppercase()
Set ambient to true to deal with noobs complaining.
Prevent null pointer exceptions when buffing/wiping kit that no longer exists.
New Kit COmaptibility + better armor parsing supporting, name, lore etc.
